{
  "stem": "26609.13",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you, yourself, because you told-- I told them that I'm not from here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm from Brody.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I want to go back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she said the best things for the people, you go-- I'll keep the child and you go out, and says outside on the street.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Said, just gather people to be sent to Germany for forced labor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So she said, you, once you'll be outside on the street and nowhere else to go, I'm sure that they will take you.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Just-- you have to do it and send you to Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because they-- if people were unemployed on the streets, they surrounded them and send them to Germany, forced labor.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So all the same, I didn't know where, why-- I know, of course, Germany [BACKGROUND NOISE] and what will happen there, and if not for a certain death.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But she didn't want to keep me anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I left the child, without a word, without saying anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She didn't let me even go near to her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Said, just go out, quickly go out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in '42.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Could be, because it was already warm and it wasn't so cold.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I delivered her to the hospital, it was cold, winter.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that could be it was springtime.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never thought of an Easter there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that's why they took me later, as I said, to that place where they gathered people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had to have such a-- a number of people to send to Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were frozen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The ones underneath, because it was warm, the top covered them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think that anyone told that story, any survivor, because no one had see.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
